"{\"uid\": \"skift.com-2024-07-11-paris-olympics-non-bump-a-17-hour-flight-and-marriotts-biz-travel-portal\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Photo Credit: Interior of Paris' Gare du Nord train station with the Olympic rings hanging from the ceiling.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 26, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999967292297, \"rank\": 3.2706583898622017e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Skift  Today's podcast looks at the Olympics' small foreign impact, new routes from Perth to Paris, and Marriott's new online travel booking tool.\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 256, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 194, \"end\": 199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\", \"score\": 0.9999563265411041, \"rank\": 4.36574682052618e-05, \"text\": \"Perth\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\"}, {\"begin\": 203, \"end\": 208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999967292297, \"rank\": 3.2706583898622017e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 214, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\", \"score\": 0.9999997215530062, \"rank\": 2.7844708180912447e-07, \"text\": \"Marriott\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Skift Travel Podcasts  Good morning from Skift.\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 299, \"end\": 304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skift\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Skift\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skift\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's Thursday, July 11, and here's what you need to know about the business of travel today.\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Apple Podcasts|Spotify|Overcast|Google Podcasts  Paris is expecting to see a small bump in overseas visitorsfor the upcoming Summer Olympics, but no large-scale boom, writes Global Tourism Reporter Dawit Habtemariam.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999967292297, \"rank\": 3.2706583898622017e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Less than 15% of the projected roughly 11 million Olympic visitors will be foreign, according to the city's tourism board.\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris tourism chief Corinne Menegaux had previously told us that most Olympic ticket holders will be French.\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 741, \"end\": 746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999967292297, \"rank\": 3.2706583898622017e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 761, \"end\": 768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corinne_Skinner-Carter\", \"score\": 0.9941814251424825, \"rank\": 0.005839305855511517, \"text\": \"Corinne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corinne_Skinner-Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corinne_Skinner-Carter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Habtemariam notes many travelers are avoiding the popular tourist destination because of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, international flight bookings to Paris for the Olympic period - from July 26 to August 11 - have increased by 8% from the same timeframe last year.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 998, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999967292297, \"rank\": 3.2706583898622017e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That figure is a substantial decrease from the last pre-Covid Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Next, speaking of the French capital, Qantas will debut a roughly 17-hour nonstopflight from Perth to Parison Friday, writes Airlines Editor Gordon Smith and Reporter Pranjal Pande.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9992524784376164, \"rank\": 0.0005968337824940108, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1231, \"end\": 1237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.155990763073686e-19, \"text\": \"Qantas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\"}, {\"begin\": 1286, \"end\": 1291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\", \"score\": 0.9999563265411041, \"rank\": 4.36574682052618e-05, \"text\": \"Perth\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\"}, {\"begin\": 1334, \"end\": 1346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gordon_H._Smith\", \"score\": 0.9999999929907517, \"rank\": 7.009309945152006e-09, \"text\": \"Gordon Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gordon_H._Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gordon_H._Smith\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Perth-Paris flights will operate four times a week prior to the second week of August, after which flights between the two cities will operate three times a week.\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Qantas currently operates ultra-long-haul flights from Perth to both London and Rome.\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1543, \"end\": 1549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.155990763073686e-19, \"text\": \"Qantas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qantas\"}, {\"begin\": 1598, \"end\": 1603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\", \"score\": 0.9999563265411041, \"rank\": 4.36574682052618e-05, \"text\": \"Perth\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Perth\"}, {\"begin\": 1612, \"end\": 1618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999770988034307, \"rank\": 2.2889731300290798e-05, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1623, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"score\": 0.8877390174571385, \"rank\": 0.11549273771512887, \"text\": \"Rome\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The company has said that roughly nine in every 10 seats on its Perth-London route have been occupied.\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally, Senior Hospitality Editor Sean O'Neill provides more information aboutMarriott's new online travel booking portalfor small- to medium-sized businesses.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Se\\u00e1n_O'Neill\", \"score\": 0.559997636474702, \"rank\": 0.38095238095234807, \"text\": \"Sean O'Neill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Se\\u00e1n_O'Neill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Se\\u00e1n_O'Neill\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The new booking platform is part of Marriott's strategy to increase direct bookings from corporate travelers.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 2004, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1931, \"end\": 1939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\", \"score\": 0.9999997215530062, \"rank\": 2.7844708180912447e-07, \"text\": \"Marriott\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Marriott executive said existing booking tools do not satisfy the needs of business travelers.\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2101, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2007, \"end\": 2015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\", \"score\": 0.9999997215530062, \"rank\": 2.7844708180912447e-07, \"text\": \"Marriott\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Small- and medium-sized businesses have become a larger part of the company's guest mix coming out of the pandemic.\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Neill notes Marriott sees an opportunity to simplify the often complicated business travel process, with companies increasingly looking for more efficient solutions.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2218, \"end\": 2225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eugene_O'Neill\", \"score\": 0.9998649787502076, \"rank\": 0.00010328843205169161, \"text\": \"O'Neill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eugene_O'Neill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eugene_O'Neill\"}, {\"begin\": 2232, \"end\": 2240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\", \"score\": 0.9999997215530062, \"rank\": 2.7844708180912447e-07, \"text\": \"Marriott\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Presenter/Producer: Jane Alexander  Curated byDennis Schaal  Executive Editor  Per Diemis your source for the latest business travel and corporate travel news.\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2546, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2407, \"end\": 2421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jane_Alexander\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.153726276210486e-14, \"text\": \"Jane Alexander\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jane_Alexander\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jane_Alexander\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get it in your inbox every Tuesday.\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By submitting this form, you agree to receive email communication from Skift.\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2656, \"end\": 2661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skift\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Skift\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skift\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tags:business travel,marriott,olympics,paris,qantas,skift daily briefing,skift podcast\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2685, \"end\": 2693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\", \"score\": 0.9999997215530062, \"rank\": 2.7844708180912447e-07, \"text\": \"marriott\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marriott_International\"}]}]}"